Package de.feu.massim22.group3.map

Interface INaviAgentV2

All Superinterfaces:
Disposable, INavi
All Known Implementing Classes:
Navi
public interface INaviAgentV2 extends INavi
The Interface INaviAgentV2 defines methods for special interaction between BdiAgentV2 and the Navi.

Heinz Stadler, Melinda Betz (minor contribution)

    • updateMap

      void updateMap(String supervisor, String agent, int agentIndex, Point position, int vision, Set<massim.protocol.data.Thing> things, List<Point> goalPoints, List<Point> rolePoints, int step, String team, int maxSteps, int score, Set<massim.protocol.data.NormInfo> normsInfo, Set<massim.protocol.data.TaskInfo> taskInfo, List<Point> attachedPoints)
      Saves data from an agent received in the current step into the GameMap.
      Parameters:
      supervisor - the name of the supervisor of the group the agent is part of
      agent - the name of the agent
      agentIndex - the index of the agent
      position - the current position of the agent
      vision - the size of the vision of the agent
      things - the things which are currently in vision
      goalPoints - the goal points which are currently in vision
      rolePoints - the role points which are currently in vision
      step - the current step of the simulation
      team - the name of the team the agent is part of
      maxSteps - the number of steps the match has
      score - the current score of the team
      normsInfo - the current active norms
      taskInfo - the current active tasks
      attachedPoints - the attached points of the agent
